    <div class="container">
        <section id="introduction">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to the Audio to Summary project. This tool allows you to convert audio from video files into text summaries using advanced speech recognition technologies.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="installation">
            <h2>Installation</h2>
            <p>Follow these steps to install the necessary dependencies and set up the project:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Clone the repository:
                    <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/yourusername/audio-to-summary.git</code></pre>
                </li>
                <li>Navigate to the project directory:
                    <pre><code>cd audio-to-summary</code></pre>
                </li>
                <li>Install the required Python packages:
                    <pre><code>pip install -r requirements.txt</code></pre>
                </li>
                <li>Ensure you have FFMPEG installed and added to your system PATH.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section id="usage">
            <h2>Usage</h2>
            <p>To use the tool, follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Place your MP4 video file in the project directory.</li>
                <li>Run the script to extract audio and convert it to text:
                    <pre><code>python main.py path_to_your_video_file.mp4</code></pre>
                </li>
                <li>The transcribed text will be displayed in the console.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section id="troubleshooting">
            <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
            <p>If you encounter any issues, consider the following solutions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Ensure that FFMPEG is installed and added to your system PATH.</li>
                <li>Check your internet connection if you are using online speech recognition services.</li>
                <li>Verify that the video file is not corrupted and is accessible.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@audio-to-summary.com">support@audio-to-summary.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Audio to Summary &copy; 2023</p>
    </footer>
</body>